{
  "texts": [
    "Also, these systems can benefit from learning words from two different languages in different training instances.",
    "We conducted two types of fine-tuning: direct fine-tuning and continuous training.",
    "Direct fine-tuning entails using concatenated data from previously constructed augmented datasets, such as the CRAFT EN + ES dataset.",
    "This fine-tuning strategy simply employs one system and one dataset to produce a single output, thus no additional training or fine-tuning is required.",
    "Continuous training, on the other hand, entails fine-tuning a model with an initial dataset, e.g."
  ]
}